Project Title

AI Interview Preparation Platform

Project Overview

The AI Interview Preparation Platform is a web-based application that helps students and job seekers prepare for interviews using Artificial Intelligence. The platform conducts mock interviews, asks technical and HR questions, evaluates user responses, and provides instant feedback. It also tracks performance, identifies weak areas, and suggests improvements to increase interview confidence and placement success.

Problem Statement

Many students and job seekers struggle to perform well in interviews due to lack of practice, confidence, and personalized guidance. Traditional interview preparation methods do not provide real-time feedback or simulate actual interview environments effectively. There is a need for an intelligent platform that can conduct mock interviews, evaluate answers, and provide personalized recommendations to help candidates improve their communication, technical knowledge, and interview performance.

Technologies
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React
Backend: Java, Spring Boot
Database: MySQL
AI Integration: Speech Recognition, Natural Language Processing (NLP), AI-based Answer Evaluation
